props.synopsis: The Northern Land Council says the four men landed on Australia's northern coastline on Monday.

title.children: Four foreign nationals found on Croker Island say they paid money to be taken to Australia

image.altText: An image of a small carpark next to a Middle Arm boat ramp.

props.synopsis: The NT government has pushed back the timeline for its planned Middle Arm industrial hub, after federal government body Infrastructure Australia rejected its business case.

title.children: Controversial planned NT gas hub could face lengthy delays after business case sent back for more work

image.altText: A woman looks into the camera inside her home, with a framed photo of her son on the wall behind her.

props.synopsis: Samara Laverty wants to make sure what happened to her son Declan never happens to anyone else. But experts say ‘Declan’s Law’ could have unintended consequences which won’t make the community safer.

title.children: Declan Laverty was murdered by a man out on bail. Will tougher bail laws prevent another tragedy?

image.altText: A man looks into the camera wearing a read and black sports club shirt.

props.synopsis: Tiwi Bombers are bouncing back from the brink, turning on electrifying performances in the NT Football League. A former Richmond Tiger is giving them a hand.

title.children: The Tiwi Bombers hit rock bottom in 2023. Now an AFL winner is helping turn it around

image.altText: An Aboriginal woman holding up a piece of fabric with artwork on it

image.altText: A young Aboriginal man leans forward on the white rodeo arena railing and stares at the camera. He wears green prison garb.

image.altText: A woman holds a trophy aloft as people look on in Italy.

props.synopsis: When you hit the water from 20 metres up and are moving at 85 kilometres per hour there is no room for error. Rhiannan Iffland has turned doing it with dominance into an art form.

image.altText: Prime Minister wears glasses and suit standing outside for press conference.

image.altText: The outside of the County Court of Victoria building.

image.altText: A man in a suit looks on, with chin resting on his hand. He is seen from close, with only his head, shoulders and hand visible

image.altText: Man in striped suit walking down steps

image.altText: A man in a light-colured suit walks past a TV cameras operator.

image.altText: A screenshot of a map, showing the location of an earthquake.

image.altText: A  stadium with a large lit up sign that says COP29 in white writing.

image.altText: A grainy, dark picture of two young girls smiling, wearing warm caps.

image.altText: Shark bites a seal shaped decoy

image.altText: Cricket Australia CEO Nick Hockley, wearing a suit jacket, no tie, speaking at a press conference at the MCG during the day

image.altText: a man in a black sweater leans against the front door of his house

image.altText: An elderly couple down a mall with the help of a younger woman.

image.altText: A man's hand holds a phone. A row of silos are in the background.

image.altText: An image of what appears to be aircraft debris.

image.altText: Ice formations resembling tiny fern trees of snow poking out from the Antarctic ice sheet with the sun dominating the background

image.altText: man wearing glasses and black suit mid shot with blue and white flags in background

image.altText: Close up of Donald Trump and Vladimir Putin in conversation

image.altText: Donald Trump smiles as he stands in front of an American flag.

props.synopsis: Donald Trump's re-election was a revolt against economic policies that have left millions disenfranchised and uncertain about their place in the world. But Americans should be wary of his policies pushing inflation and debt even higher.

image.altText: A girl with a bowl on her head walking past an airport with debris scattered in front.

props.synopsis: The airline has said one flight attendant was injured in the incident but no passengers were injured.

image.altText: Players grapple with each other

image.altText: Uranus

image.altText: A garage on fire at night on a suburban street in Sydney.

image.altText: A boy lays in a hammock above dirty flood water. His feet hang in the water.

image.altText: a human-like female robot with a bob in front of a blotchy surreal portrait of a man

image.altText: The Collingwood Football Club logo - a black magpie - on a sign.
